"{\"uid\": \"nbcbayarea.com-paris-2024-summer-olympics-usa-australia-mens-water-polo-quarterfinals-3618348\", \"text\": \"The U.S. men's water polo team, which features several players with Bay Area ties, is moving on to the semifinals at theParis Olympicsfollowing a thrilling shootout victory over Australia Wednesday.  Cal's Adrian Weinberg came up clutch in the shootout, stopping two shots from finding the back of the net.  Watch NBC Bay Area News free wherever you are  Team USA will play in the semifinals on Friday.    \"}"